metadata.description:
It’s the year 2?23. The Travelers are 1,111 carefully selected individuals considered humanity’s last hope against the mysterious Invaders who took over planet Earth, enslaved its population, and destroyed all art & culture. 

The Travelers are pillars of the Monuverse project as they represent the latest attempt to recreate the world’s cultural heritage and save it immutably on the blockchain as the only way to prevent it from being forgotten.
metadata.name: Signal Corps #48
